Package: LSSPCA
Type: Package
Title: Computes Least Squares Sparse Principal Components
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Giovanni Maria Merola
Maintainer: Giovanni Maria Merola <giovanni.merola@xjtlu.edu.cn>
Description: It provides a single function for computing the SPCs. 
